data.title: Friends are complimentary
data.meta_description: Photograph was edited for publication purposesPhotograph caption dated August 9, 1955 reads "Aldo Ray's abalone appetizers are very popular among his friends and the recipe is much in demand. Here he and his wife Jeff Donnell raid the freezer in their Valley home."
